          "name_loc": "Hydra's Breath",
          "desc_loc": "<h1>Passive: Miasma</h1>Attacks poison enemies, dealing %poison_damage_per_second%%% of the target's Max HP as Magical Damage per second for %poison_duration% seconds.\n\n<h1>Passive: Polycephaly</h1>Ranged attacks have a %proc_chance%%% chance to fire additional projectiles at up to %count% nearby enemies with %secondary_target_range_bonus% extra range and within a %secondary_target_angle% degree angle in front of the attacker. The additional projectiles deal %base_proc_dmg% + %proc_dmg_pct%%% damage of a normal attack and do not trigger on hit effects except for Miasma. The primary attack deals %base_proc_dmg% + %proc_dmg_pct_primary_tooltip%%% damage of a normal attack.",
